I think the only place where sprite flips doesn't work as expected is on unofficial sprite sizes on the SNES.<br />You can get I think 16x32 and 32x64 pixels sprites on the SNES, but this is "unofficial", and trying to flip them will flip two halves like Koitsu described instead of flipping the entire sprite.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38">Bregalad</a> — Mon May 28, 2012 12:24 pm</p><hr />
