<title type="html"><![CDATA[8x16 sprites vs. 8x8 and Y position]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=8950&amp;p=94712#p94712"><![CDATA[
Flipping doesn't affect the coordinates of a sprite in any way. The area occupied by the sprite is the same, only the contents of that area (i.e. the patterns) are modified.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=95">tokumaru</a> — Mon May 28, 2012 11:30 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
