Did you look on the wiki for how <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Sprites" class="postlink">sprites</a> work?<br /><br />As for the specific question: Flipping does not change the position of the sprite's bounding box, just the position of pixels within the sprite.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Mon May 28, 2012 4:35 am</p><hr />
